I found out what [swesub] means after I downloaded this one.  Sewdish sub-titles.  They cannot be turned off, either - they have been merged into the image (it's not like a DVD where you can choose not to display them).  The audio is still in English, so if you aren't bothered by the writing then go for it.  The video quality is decent.
